The water connections start completed and must be flipped so they return to their normal starting position.
This was part of the surprise challenge at Russia's Nationals. See a team completing the challenge: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xLU5du7bABA&ab_channel=A%D0%BB%D0%B5%D0%BA%D1%81%D0%B0%D0%BD%D0%B4%D1%80%D0%9C%D0%B0%D0%BD%D0%B4%D1%80%D0%BE%D0%BD